    "body": "closing as it turns out it is just a mandatory requirement to specify a WS rpc when using `--subscribe`:\r\n```bash\r\ncast logs --subscribe 'Subscribed(address,uint256,uint256,address)' --rpc-url ws://127.0.0.1:8545\r\n```\r\n\r\nMight be worth adding this requirement to the docs",
